Package GUIElements

Class SaveDialog

java.lang.Object
GUIElements.GUIElement
GUIElements.Container
GUIElements.Dialog
GUIElements.SaveDialog
All Implemented Interfaces:
ScrollBarListener
public class SaveDialog
extends Dialog
Dialog used to save a page. Contains one textBoxes (to enter the name of the file) and two buttons (one to cancel and return to the main dialog, and one to save).
